{"tid":55518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新支架貴近倍　保柏拒認考慮成本","createTime":"2016-12-26T13:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T04:00:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abdb3d28e64b8ef6ca36c720a9bcc283ff638bf5","tid":55518,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19877129&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19877129%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161226&d=LPJKfcuqLuhsPVaPwbkrtRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=9c11c70f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19877129%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161226&h=d5110e17\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19877129&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161226</a><br />\n<br />\n新支架貴近倍　保柏拒認考慮成本<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■保柏列為不保的最新款Abbott GT1全吸收生物血管模架。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次被保柏醫療拒賠的六款通波仔用支架，包括2012年才面世的最新「全吸收生物血管模架」，其價錢介乎3萬至3.5萬元，較上一代滲藥性支架貴近一倍。但保柏否認拒賠決定與成本有關，堅持純粹是因為新支架欠缺臨床實證證明有效。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學內科學系心臟科專科臨床助理教授陳栢羲解釋，通波仔手術是指因心血管阻塞而做的冠狀動脈介入治療，醫生通過導管把球囊置入血管堵塞位置，然後讓球囊充氣以擴張血管，手術時並會植入支架，以支撐起被球囊撐大的血管位置，維持血管暢通。<br />\n<br />\n價錢逾3萬他指，心血管支架可分為三大類別，包括傳統金屬支架、滲藥性支架及全吸收生物血管模架。最傳統舊式金屬支架有可能因內皮細胞增生而再令血管收窄，復發率約10至20%。至2002年，有滲藥性支架出現，上面含有聚合物，令置入後可慢慢釋放藥物，減低阻塞風險。但不論是金屬支架還是滲藥性支架，均會有部份金屬支架永久留在體內。<br />\n<br />\n至2012年，最新的全吸收生物血管模架世面，該支架可在3年內完全溶解，令血管回復彈性，適合年輕病人及沒有鈣化情況的病人使用，但價錢達3萬元以上。<br />\n<br />\n■記者龔蕙芝<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;醫生斥干預專業　損害病人<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;市建局研轉移地積比　重建油旺舊區"},{"pid":"8c704e84a92036acdf5b513b73cb8d7c49ceeeb2","tid":55518,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcae58769ce661a63d53fc5c57b22c471773e230","tid":55518,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"咩到唔陪，食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩冇用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92cd80365c4acf87e7d8eff03c924e89b7a67e0","tid":55518,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩<span style=\"color: red;\">都</span>唔陪，食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩冇用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"75b88d2ed17e82acb355842d5cd698a5686164e7","tid":55518,"uid":57006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n至2012年，最新的全吸收生物血管模架世面，該支架可在3年內完全<span style=\"color: red;\">溶解</span>，令血管回復彈性，適合年輕病人及沒有鈣化情況的病人使用，但價錢達3萬元以上。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n溶解時會否產生碎片?<br />\n會唔會導致中風?<br />\n點樣避免?<br />\n<br />\n有無人解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5935d1410fbf02e34f08802ccdb04a590b0ea33","tid":55518,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n至2012年，最新的全吸收生物血管模架世面，該支架可在3年內完全<span style=\"color: red;\">溶解</span>，令血管回復彈性，適合年輕病人及沒有鈣化情況的病人使用，但價錢達3萬元以上。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n溶解時會否產生碎片?<br />\n會唔會導致中風?<br />\n點樣避免?<br />\n<br />\n有無人解答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係驚有意外先買保險"},{"pid":"d76465f8db70c31caddedd4411c369f8e5267f3f","ti